text: Kadeeded () is a comedy variety show that first aired on Saturday September 9, 2000 on Channel 7 HD by Kantana Group Public Company Limited incollaboration with Imagination Rim Company Limited. Produced this show Broadcast every Saturday from 1:15 PM. - 2:30 PM.
